hopobject.body: What company are you calling from? healthyvial.com Health privacy expert McGraw said "the worst case scenario"of not meeting the IT security deadline is that the governmentwill not be able to bring the data hub online on Oct. 1. In thatcase, people will be able to apply for insurance starting onthat date but will not be told if they have been accepted orwhether they are eligible for government subsidies to pay theirpremiums.
